From 448e28c41f7096197164bdc58d23c150c04ec8af Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Fri, 10 Jul 2026 05:00:10 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add ecommerce: cart, checkout, and Stripe payment flow

- Cart context with localStorage persistence, qty controls, slide-out drawer
- Add-to-cart buttons on service cards; cart badge in header
- /checkout page with customer form and order summary
- /api/checkout route creating Stripe Checkout Sessions with
  server-side price lookup (client can never set prices)
- Demo mode when STRIPE_SECRET_KEY is unset so the flow works
  out of the box; /checkout/success confirmation page
- Styles matching the existing neo-brutalist design system
